&lt;p&gt;Client-facing and confident, you demonstrate expertise and assurance in all client interactions. Your superior social and interpersonal skills enable you to work autonomously while adeptly navigating collaborative dynamics and effectively &#39;managing up&#39; when necessary.&lt;/p&gt;
